{"about_the_game":"<strong>Will You Survive?</strong><br>Can you navigate the zombie outbreak and find a way out of this nightmare? Stale Nation puts you in the shoes of Thomas, a young man who arrives back from spending months on a hiking trip to find that the world around him has been plunged into chaos. Zombies now roam the world seeking nothing more than to kill all of the survivors. Sneak by the zombies, learn more about what happened, and escape in this zombie walking simulator game created by a solo developer.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282190/extras/zombie_gif.gif?t=1691458629\" /><br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Zombies that chase you down if they notice you.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Stealth mechanics that force you to think about how you move around the infected.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A deep, immersive story that is captivating and chilling.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A journal to keep track of things you have learned and read about.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282190/extras/ezgif-5-0d2527c6e3.gif?t=1691458629\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282190/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1691458629","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282190/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1691458629","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282190/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1691458629","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282190/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1691458629","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":"This game contains scenes of violence and graphic material such as blood, guts and corpses. "},"det